# SOCIALCLUB::SC_EMAIL_GET_RETRIEVAL_STATUS

## Summary
Returns the retrieval status after SC_EMAIL_RETRIEVE_EMAILS has been called

## Returns
* **eEMAIL_RETRIEVAL_STATUS**
